      • bindingsFromDataTable

        public static java.util.List<ExtendedBinding> bindingsFromDataTable(DataTable bindingsTable,
                                                                    @Nullable
                                                                    Pinpoint pinpoint)
                                                             throws SyntaxErrorException
        Converts given bindings table into a list of extended binding instances assuming that the table has appropriate format.
        Parameters:
        bindingsTable - source table to read bindings data from
        pinpoint - an optional pointer to the place where the bindings belong to (e.g. a context's variable)
        Returns:
        a list of instantiated bindings and their options
        Throws:
        SyntaxErrorException - if some of the bindings contain a malformed expression
